            </div>

        </header>

        <main>
            <section id="home">
                <p class="main-paragraph">Welcome to CelebrateMate, where every moment is a reason to rejoice! In our fast-paced lives, it's easy to lose track of those special occasions that bring joy and connection. That's where CelebrateMate steps in â€“ your trusted companion for automated birthday and anniversary reminders. Say goodbye to missed celebrations and hello to heartfelt connections, as CelebrateMate ensures you never forget a cherished moment with your loved ones.</p>

                    <form class="profile-form" id="profileForm">
    
                        <div class="segment profile-form-text">
                        <h1>Create Your Profile</h1>
                        </div>

                        <label class="profile-form-label" for="name">
                            <input type="text" placeholder="Name" class="profile-form-input" id="name" name="name" required/>
                        </label>
                        <label class="profile-form-label" for="birthdate"> <p class="profile-form-birthdate profile-form-text">Birthdate:</p>
                            <input type="date" class="profile-form-input" id="birthdate" name="birthdate" required/>
                        </label>
                        <label class="profile-form-label" for="email">
                            <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="profile-form-input" id="email" name="email" required/>
                        </label>
                        <label class="profile-form-label" for="phone">
                            <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" class="profile-form-input" id="phone" name="phone" required/>
                        </label>

                        <button class="color profile-form-button" type="submit"><i class="icon ion-md-lock"></i>Submit Profile</button>

                    </form>

                <div  id="website_inside" class="hidden">
                    <br><br>
                    
                    <div class="single-item">
                        <div>
                            <span>Personalized Message</span>
                            <p>Send a handwritten letter or a heartfelt message to express your appreciation. Personal touches make all the difference!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Customized Gifts</span>
                            <p>Create a custom gift like a photo album, a scrapbook, or a personalized piece of jewelry. It shows thoughtfulness and care.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Surprise Party</span>
                            <p>Organize a surprise party with close friends and family. Plan some fun activities and make it a memorable event.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Memory Lane</span>
                            <p>Create a scrapbook or a digital slideshow of cherished moments together. Include photos, tickets, and notes.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Special Meal</span>
                            <p>Cook their favorite meal or dine at a special restaurant. Consider a themed dinner or a picnic in a scenic location.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Handmade Gifts</span>
                            <p>Create something with your own hands, like a knitted scarf, a piece of pottery, or a hand-painted picture.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Adventure Day</span>
                            <p>Plan a day full of adventure activities such as hiking, kayaking, or exploring a new city together.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Time Capsule</span>
                            <p>Create a time capsule with items that are meaningful to your relationship. Plan to open it together on a future date.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2 class="rainbow-text">Add A New Event!</h2>
                    <br>

                        <div class="home-container">

                            <div class="add-event">
                                <form id="contactForm">
                                    <input placeholder="Name" for="contactName" id="contactName" name="contactName" type="text" class="event-form-input" required/>
                                    <label for="eventType">Event Type:</label>
                                        <select id="eventType" name="eventType" class="event-form-select">
                                            <option value="birthday">Birthday</option>
                                            <option value="anniversary">Anniversary</option>
                                        </select><br><br>
                                    <label for="date">Date:</label>
                                    <input type="date" id="date" name="date" required class="event-form-input">
                                    <input placeholder="Email" for="email" id="email" name="email" type="email" class="event-form-input" required/>
                                    <br><br>
                                    <button type="submit" class="event-form-button">Add Event</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>

                            <div class="ready-made-message">
                                <h1 class="rainbow-text" style="text-align: right;">Pre-written message ready for dispatch!</h1>
                                <br>
                                <% if(profileData.length > 0)
                                {
                                %>
                                <form class="message-form" id="messageForm">
                                <fieldset id="messageContent" name="fullMessage">
                                    <p>Hey, <select name="contactName">
                                        <% if(eventsResult.length > 0)
                                            {
                                                eventsResult.forEach(entry => { %>
                                                    <option><%= entry.contactName %></option>
                                                    <%
                                                    }
                                                );
                                            }
                                        %>
                                    </select></p>
                                    <p>Just wanted to take a moment to wish you a very Happy <select>
                                        <option>Birthday</option>
                                        <option>Anniversary</option>
                                    </select>.</p>
                                    <p>I hope your day is filled with <span class="form__field field--message" data-placeholder="joy" tabindex="1" contenteditable></span> and <span class="form__field field--message" data-placeholder="laughter" tabindex="2" contenteditable></span>.</p>
                                    <p>Take care and stay <span class="form__field field--message" data-placeholder="awesome" tabindex="3" contenteditable></span>!</p>
                                    <p>Warm regards,</p>
                                    <p><span class="form__field field--message" data-placeholder="<%= profileData[0].name %>" tabindex="4" contenteditable></span></p>
                                    <button type="submit" class="button button--xlarge" tabindex="5">Send message &#187;</button>
                                </fieldset>
                                <input type="hidden" name="fullMessage" id="fullMessage">
                                </form>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        
