                                <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="0 20" />
                            </filter>
                            </defs>
                        </svg>

                </div>

            </section>

            <section id="about" class="hidden">
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem;">Imagine a world where every special occasion is met with excitement and anticipation, where no birthday goes unnoticed and no anniversary is left uncelebrated. With CelebrateMate, that world becomes a reality. Our user-friendly interface allows you to effortlessly set up personalized profiles for yourself and your contacts, ensuring that important dates are never overlooked. From customizable notifications to seamless integration with your existing contact lists and calendars, CelebrateMate is your all-in-one solution for staying connected and celebrating life's precious moments. At CelebrateMate, we understand the importance of staying connected with the people who matter most. That's why we've designed a seamless web application that not only sends timely reminders but also offers thoughtful suggestions for meaningful ways to celebrate. Whether it's a birthday, anniversary, or any other milestone, CelebrateMate is here to help you make every moment count, fostering stronger relationships and deeper connections along the way.</p>
                <br>
                <div id="infostrip" style="background:teal;">
                    <h1>Personalized Profiles<hr></h1>
