                    </symbol></use></svg>
                    <p> Our Personalized Profiles feature allows you to manage special occasions with ease. By creating a profile, you can enter your name, birthday, email, and phone number, which helps us provide a tailored experience just for you. Once your profile is set up, you can add events like birthdays and anniversaries, keeping all important dates in one place. CelebrateMate sends you timely notifications via phone and email, reminding you of upcoming celebrations, so you never miss a special moment. Additionally, on your birthday, youâ€™ll receive a personalized happy birthday message, ensuring you feel celebrated and appreciated on your special day. </p>
                </div>
                    
                <div id="infostrip" style="background:#7d5056f7;">
                    <h1>Add Event Form<hr></h1>
                    <svg class="about-icon icon-fire"><use xlink:href="#icon-fire"><symbol id="icon-fire" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                    <title>fire</title>
                    <path d="M10.031 32c-2.133-4.438-0.997-6.981 0.642-9.376 1.795-2.624 2.258-5.221 2.258-5.221s1.411 1.834 0.847 4.703c2.493-2.775 2.963-7.196 2.587-8.889 5.635 3.938 8.043 12.464 4.798 18.783 17.262-9.767 4.294-24.38 2.036-26.027 0.753 1.646 0.895 4.433-0.625 5.785-2.573-9.759-8.937-11.759-8.937-11.759 0.753 5.033-2.728 10.536-6.084 14.648-0.118-2.007-0.243-3.392-1.298-5.312-0.237 3.646-3.023 6.617-3.777 10.27-1.022 4.946 0.765 8.568 7.555 12.394z"></path>
                    </symbol></use></svg>
                    <p> Our Add Event Form is a simple and intuitive tool where you can input all the necessary details about a personâ€™s special event. You can add their contact information, name, specify the type of event (whether it's a birthday or an anniversary), the date of the event, and their email address. This email will be used to send a customized message from our ready-made message template. This ensures that your wishes are timely and heartfelt, without the hassle of remembering dates or drafting messages. </p>
                </div>
                    
                    
                <div id="infostrip" style="background:#4c4c4c;">
                    <h1>Event Board<hr></h1>
                    <svg class="about-icon icon-bug"><use xlink:href="#icon-bug"></use><symbol id="icon-bug" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                    <title>bug</title>
                    <path d="M32 18v-2h-6.040c-0.183-2.271-0.993-4.345-2.24-6.008h5.061l2.189-8.758-1.94-0.485-1.811 7.242h-5.459c-0.028-0.022-0.056-0.043-0.084-0.064 0.21-0.609 0.324-1.263 0.324-1.944 0-3.305-2.686-5.984-6-5.984s-6 2.679-6 5.984c0 0.68 0.114 1.334 0.324 1.944-0.028 0.021-0.056 0.043-0.084 0.064h-5.459l-1.811-7.242-1.94 0.485 2.189 8.758h5.061c-1.246 1.663-2.056 3.736-2.24 6.008h-6.040v2h6.043c0.119 1.427 0.485 2.775 1.051 3.992h-3.875l-2.189 8.757 1.94 0.485 1.811-7.243h3.511c1.834 2.439 4.606 3.992 7.708 3.992s5.874-1.554 7.708-3.992h3.511l1.811 7.243 1.94-0.485-2.189-8.757h-3.875c0.567-1.217 0.932-2.565 1.051-3.992h6.043z"></path>
                    </symbol></svg>
                    <p> The Event Board is where all your added events are stored and displayed like sticky notes on a digital bulletin board. Each sticky note contains the details of an individual event, making it easy to see and manage upcoming celebrations. Birthdays are organized in order of occurrence, so you can see whose birthday is coming up next at a glance. This visual representation helps you stay organized and ensures you never miss an important date. </p>
                </div>

                <div id="infostrip" style="background:teal;">
                    <h1>Ready-to-Send Messages<hr></h1>
                    <svg class="about-icon icon-camera" ><use xlink:href="#icon-camera"><symbol id="icon-camera" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                    <title>camera</title>
                    <path d="M9.5 19c0 3.59 2.91 6.5 6.5 6.5s6.5-2.91 6.5-6.5-2.91-6.5-6.5-6.5-6.5 2.91-6.5 6.5zM30 8h-7c-0.5-2-1-4-3-4h-8c-2 0-2.5 2-3 4h-7c-1.1 0-2 0.9-2 2v18c0 1.1 0.9 2 2 2h28c1.1 0 2-0.9 2-2v-18c0-1.1-0.9-2-2-2zM16 27.875c-4.902 0-8.875-3.973-8.875-8.875s3.973-8.875 8.875-8.875c4.902 0 8.875 3.973 8.875 8.875s-3.973 8.875-8.875 8.875zM30 14h-4v-2h4v2z"></path>
                    </symbol></use></svg>
                    <p> Our Ready-to-Send Message feature offers a convenient message box pre-filled with thoughtful lines, which you can easily personalize. You can select the recipient from your list of contacts and send the message directly to their email. This feature saves you time and ensures your messages are both personal and prompt, adding a special touch to every greeting. </p>
                </div>
                    
                <div id="infostrip" style="background:#7d5056f7;">
                    <h1>Notifications<hr></h1>
                    <svg class="about-icon icon-fire"><use xlink:href="#icon-fire"><symbol id="icon-fire" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                    <title>fire</title>
                    <path d="M10.031 32c-2.133-4.438-0.997-6.981 0.642-9.376 1.795-2.624 2.258-5.221 2.258-5.221s1.411 1.834 0.847 4.703c2.493-2.775 2.963-7.196 2.587-8.889 5.635 3.938 8.043 12.464 4.798 18.783 17.262-9.767 4.294-24.38 2.036-26.027 0.753 1.646 0.895 4.433-0.625 5.785-2.573-9.759-8.937-11.759-8.937-11.759 0.753 5.033-2.728 10.536-6.084 14.648-0.118-2.007-0.243-3.392-1.298-5.312-0.237 3.646-3.023 6.617-3.777 10.27-1.022 4.946 0.765 8.568 7.555 12.394z"></path>
                    </symbol></use></svg>
                    <p> Never miss a celebration with our Notifications feature. You will receive daily notifications on your phone and email, alerting you about upcoming birthdays or anniversaries happening today or tomorrow. This proactive reminder system ensures you are always prepared to send your best wishes on time. </p>
                </div>

                <div id="infostrip" style="background:#4c4c4c;">
                    <h1>Contact Us<hr></h1>
                    <svg class="about-icon icon-bug"><use xlink:href="#icon-bug"></use><symbol id="icon-bug" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                    <title>bug</title>
                    <path d="M32 18v-2h-6.040c-0.183-2.271-0.993-4.345-2.24-6.008h5.061l2.189-8.758-1.94-0.485-1.811 7.242h-5.459c-0.028-0.022-0.056-0.043-0.084-0.064 0.21-0.609 0.324-1.263 0.324-1.944 0-3.305-2.686-5.984-6-5.984s-6 2.679-6 5.984c0 0.68 0.114 1.334 0.324 1.944-0.028 0.021-0.056 0.043-0.084 0.064h-5.459l-1.811-7.242-1.94 0.485 2.189 8.758h5.061c-1.246 1.663-2.056 3.736-2.24 6.008h-6.040v2h6.043c0.119 1.427 0.485 2.775 1.051 3.992h-3.875l-2.189 8.757 1.94 0.485 1.811-7.243h3.511c1.834 2.439 4.606 3.992 7.708 3.992s5.874-1.554 7.708-3.992h3.511l1.811 7.243 1.94-0.485-2.189-8.757h-3.875c0.567-1.217 0.932-2.565 1.051-3.992h6.043z"></path>
                    </symbol></svg>
                    <p> At CelebrateMate, we value your feedback and are committed to providing a seamless user experience. Our Contact Us form allows you to reach out to us with any issues, suggestions, or bugs you may encounter while using our website. We are dedicated to improving our platform and appreciate your input. Your messages are important to us, and we strive to respond promptly to all inquiries. Whether it's a technical glitch or a suggestion for a new feature, your feedback helps us enhance CelebrateMate for everyone. </p>
                </div>
                    
            </section>

